replies.body:
1) Highest AP by TEN ...... after charging it up and having other Mana items. Otherwise, {{item:3089}} and {{item:3285}} win hands down. {{item:3041}} Also gives higher AP on most builds (145 AP). {{item:3907}} ALSO gives more AP, AND MOVE SPEED AND is FAR Less restrictive than {{item:3003}} 

The Charge up is the entire reason NO ONE BOUGHT IT FOR NINE YEARS.

2) High Mana doesn't matter when you have ample sources of replenishment, and the entire PURPOSE of the additional mana, was the FACT {{item:3165}}  LOST IT ({{item:3003}}  +{{item:3165}} gives the same exact Mana as it used to, and now a whopping 100 LESS AP, same CDR)

3) Shield lasts 2 seconds and has a long cooldown and is ONLY to SELF TARGET.  It's a TINY shield compared to {{item:3190}}
